outh Team's Player of the Year''' ||align=\"center\"| [[Adam Baker (footballer)|Adam Baker]]\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Bradford City A.F.C. seasons}}\n{{2011\u201312 in English football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2011-12 Bradford City A.F.C. Season}}\n[[Category:Bradford City A.F.C. seasons]]\n[[Category:2011\u201312 Football League Two by team|Bradford City]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2015}}\n{{Use British English|date=February 2015}}\n{{Infobox football club season\n| club               = [[Bradford City A.F.C.]]\n| season             = 2011\u201312\n| manager            = [[Peter Jackson (footballer born 1961)|Peter Jackson]](until 25 August 2011) <br/> [[Colin Cooper]] (caretaker until 29 August 2011) <br/> [[Phil Parkinson]]\n| chairman           = [[Mark Lawn]] <br/> [[Julian Rhodes]]\n| league             = [[2011\u201312 Football League Two|League Two]]\n| league result      = 18th\n| cup1               = [[2011\u201312 FA Cup|FA Cup]]\n| cup1 result        = 3rd Round (vs. [[Watford F.C.|Watford]])\n| cup2               = [[2011\u201312 Football League Cup|League Cup]]\n| cup2 result        = 1st Round (vs. [[Leeds United A.F.C.|Leeds United]])\n| cup3               = [[2011\u201312 Football League Trophy|Football League Trophy]]\n| cup3 result        = Area Semi Final (North) (vs. [[Oldham Athletic A.F.C.|Oldham Athletic]])\n| league topscorer   = <br/> [[James Hanson (footballer born 1987)|James Hanson]] (13)\n| season topscorer   = <br/> [[James Hanson (footballer born 1987)|James Hanson]] (14)\n| highest attendance = <br/> 17,014 vs [[Hereford United]] (League Two)\n| lowest attendance  = <br/> 3,432 vs [[AFC Wimbledon]] (FA Cup)\n| average attendance = 10,491\n| pattern_la1 =_bradford1112h|pattern_b1=_bradford1112h|pattern_ra1=_bradford1112h|\n| leftarm1 = 800000|body1=800000|rightarm1=800000|shorts1=800000|socks1=800000\n| pattern_la2=_southend1112a|pattern_b2=_southend1112a|pattern_ra2=_southend1112a\n| leftarm2 = FF0044|